{"type":"message","id":"9bc0973c","parentId":"14c693f9","timestamp":"2026-03-27T14:42:47.983Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Looking at the sessions_list result, the only session is the cron session itself (this current run). There's no active user conversation happening - all I see is this cron job session and its own messages. No real user messages in the last 5 minutes.\n\nSo I should execute the autonomous learning task:\n1. Search for latest news on enterprise digital transformation, smart security, network system integration, IT operations services - industries related to 道简网络\n2. Organize 3-5 key pieces of information\n3. Save to /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/学习笔记.md\n\nLet me search for this information first.","thinkingSignature":"8e9982e987ba73c1db12fa1cedee3bf3d3f7491d2d1f096f5bee9ad63f59a5c4"},{"type":"text","text":"检测到只有当前Cron任务会话，无真实用户活跃对话。开始执行自主学习。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_xjajv7zd39b4_1","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"task":"搜索以下4个道简网络相关行业的最新动态（2026年3月）：\n1. 企业数字化转型\n2. 智能安防/弱电工程\n3. 网络系统集成\n4. IT运维服务\n\n要求：\n- 搜索最新行业新闻、政策动态、技术趋势\n- 筛选与中国市场、ToB企业服务相关的内容\n- 整理出3-5条关键信息，每条包含：标题、摘要、来源\n- 输出格式：Markdown列表\n\n请将搜索结果直接输出，不需要写文件。","runtime":"subagent","mode":"run"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":836,"output":304,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45121,"cost":{"input":0.00025079999999999997,"output":0.0003648,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00193503}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774622558498}}
